         <abstract id="aspace_ea4d6e0fcbb8630d4adf6b2197dad762">The Wallace Thurman Collection contains Correspondence, (including letters from Langston Hughes), Writings, primarily versions of Aunt Hagar's Children and the musical play Harlem, written with William Jourdan Rapp, and Personal Papers.</abstract>
         <origination label="creator">
            <persname identifier="http://id.loc.gov/authorities/names/n50011901" source="naf">
